cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.IR 

This paper is about road extraction from satellite images using deep learning techniques. The most relevant arXiv CS sub-category is Computer Vision (cs.CV) as the paper focuses on image segmentation using Convolutional Neural Networks. The paper also discusses the use of non-local blocks to capture long-range dependencies, which is a common technique in Natural Language Processing (NLP) and falls under the sub-category of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of non-local blocks for Robotics (cs.RO) and Information Retrieval (cs.IR) tasks, but these are less likely as they are not directly related to the main focus of the paper.
